	<div data-zesty-id="content:block:6-bcfbdaa6d3-vjj3qs:27:95:0:40">{{block('/-/block/hero_full.html?variant=7-8695d6ab8a-pf02rw')}}</div>
	<div class="p-6 rounded-5 bg-light mb-18" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:39:59">
<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:39:59-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:2:27">
	<strong>How We Help</strong>
</p>
<div class="my-4" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-md:3:8"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:4:33">Brighten the Holidays</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:5:23">
	The Salvation Army Greater Birmingham Area Command brings Christmas wish lists to life through our Christmas programs.&nbsp; Your continued support is greatly appreciated.
</p>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:6:63"></div>
<div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:300px;background-image:url('https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/ba1ae43a-1116-430b-a313-47c06d536cc0_Blue+BG.png');background-position:center center;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:cover;" class="text-white rounded p-6 gap-3 my-5" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:7:7">
            <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:2;"></div>
            <div style="position:relative;z-index:3;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-start;min-height:300px;">
                <div style="width:100%;padding:40px;color:#ffffff;">
                    <div class="btgrid">
	<div class="row row-1">
		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<p style="text-align:center;color:#fff;">
					<img class="img-fluid rounded d-block mx-auto" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/3fb28876-28f7-4dd1-9bf1-5742f4f94948_9849750a-9302-45c1-b4c7-1790a4013f0a_255019820_5187182337964381_9119289557333576273_n%2B%281%29.jpg">
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="col col-md-6 col-sm-12">
			<div class="content">
				<h5 style="text-align:center;">Wbrc Fox 6 Gifts for Kids<br>
				Salvation Army Angel Tree</h5>

				<p style="text-align:center;color:#fff;">
					Wbrc Fox 6 News is proud to once again partner with The Salvation Army for our annual “Gifts for Kids Angel Tree” program.&nbsp;
				</p>

				<p style="text-align:center;color:#fff;">
					The “Gifts for Kids Angel Tree” program is a way for people to donate Christmas gifts to foster children and children in need during the holiday season. You can purchase gifts or make a financial donation to The Salvation Army Greater Birmingham Area Command. Your donation will be used to buy clothing, toys, and gifts for children participating in the Angel Tree program.&nbsp;&nbsp;
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:8:82"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:9:90">How to Help&nbsp;</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:29"><strong>There are several ways you can help:&nbsp;</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:11:49">
	<li><strong>In-person:</strong> Adopt an Angel from the Angel Tree at The Outlet Shops of Grand River or The Riverchase Galleria November 7 through December 3, 2025.</li>
	<li><strong>Online: </strong>Adopt Angels online by clicking <a href="https://www.tsamm.org/angeltree/adopt.dpi?c=4481F46BC05E466E32DA99F86F7AE526592B72DF" target="_blank">here</a>.&nbsp;Online adoptions will begin November 7. For more information, contact Regina Williams at <a href="mailto:Regina.Williams@uss.SalvationArmy.org" target="">Regina.Williams@uss.SalvationArmy.org</a> .</li>
	<li><strong>Forgotten Angels: </strong>Drop-off new, unwrapped toys or gifts at any participating area Chick-fil-A locations, November 7 – December 3, 2025.</li>
	<li><strong>Walmart Registry:</strong> Shop our Walmart Registry to purchase gifts online for Angels. Look for ‘2025 Angel Tree program Greater Birmingham Registry', and purchase from the “Wish List” for a child for Christmas. Purchases will be shipped to The Birmingham Area Command and given to a child in need for Christmas. The online registry runs October 24 - December 16, 2025. For more information, contact Regina Williams at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:Regina.Williams@uss.SalvationArmy.org" target="">Regina.Williams@uss.SalvationArmy.org</a> or <a href="tel:+12054530947" target="">205-453-0947</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;Visit the Birmingham Area Command’s Registry <a href="https://www.walmart.com/registry/RR/1b6bbf36-e2e9-410a-b87c-1175c15fe57e" target="_blank">HERE</a>.</li>
	<li><strong>Give Financially:</strong> Bring Christmas wishes to life, by supporting a child or family for the holidays. Make a financial donation at <a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/birmingham-al/waystogive" target="">BirminghamSalvationArmy.org</a> and click the “<a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/birmingham-al/waystogive" target="">Ways to Give</a>” tab.&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>Serve with Us:</strong> Volunteers are the Army behind The Army, and are an important part of #DoingTheMostGood this holiday season.&nbsp; If you or your organization would like to volunteer with us, click&nbsp;<a href="https://bttr.im/dp910" target="">here</a>&nbsp;for more information.</li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:12:53"></div>
