<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:18:30">Corporate Angel Tree</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:19:17">
	For more information on Corporate Angel Tree, please contact Darlene Ray at <a href="mailto:Darlene.Ray@uss.SalvationArmy.org" target="">Darlene.Ray@uss.SalvationArmy.org</a>.
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:20:49"></div>
<div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:300px;background-image:url('https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/ba1ae43a-1116-430b-a313-47c06d536cc0_Blue+BG.png');background-position:center center;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:cover;" class="text-white rounded p-6 gap-3 my-5" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:22:93">
