            <div style="position:relative;z-index:3;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-start;min-height:300px;">
                <div style="width:100%;padding:40px;color:#ffffff;">
                    <h5 style="text-align:center;">Red Kettles&nbsp; &nbsp;</h5>

<p style="text-align:center;color:#fff;">
	<strong>&nbsp;</strong>The iconic #Red Kettles of The Salvation Army support the programs and services of The Salvation Army Greater Birmingham Area Command.&nbsp; The 2023 Red Kettle Season kicks off November 17.&nbsp;&nbsp; If you are interested in volunteering as a Bell Ringer, please contact Major Bret McElroy at <a href="tel: 205-948-0017"> 205-948-0017 </a> or <a href="mailto:Bret.McElroy@uss.SalvationArmy.org" target="">Bret.McElroy@uss.SalvationArmy.org</a>.&nbsp; &nbsp;
</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:23:19"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:25:24">Round-Up At the Register</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:26:64">
	Is your business looking for a way to give back this holiday season?&nbsp; 'Round Up at the Register' is an easy way you and your customers can support the programs and services at The Salvation Army Greater Birmingham Area Command!&nbsp; If you have a retail business that is interested in participating, please contact <strong>Major Bret McElroy at <a href="mailto:Bret.McElroy@uss.SalvationArmy.org" target="">Bret.McElroy@uss.SalvationArmy.org</a> or <a href="tel: 205-734-3143"> 205-734.3143</a>.</strong>
</p>
